      <section eId="sec_40_4_40">
        <num>40-4-40</num>
        <content>
          <p>Any person who purchases a used motor vehicle or any used part comprising a component part of any motor vehicle for resale shall keep an accurate record of the date of purchase, the price paid, and the name and address of the person from whom the vehicle or part is purchased. Such information shall be maintained in permanent records for a period of not less than one year and shall be open to inspection by appropriate law enforcement officers.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1963, p. 436, ยง 1.)</p>
